<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat <expan>dis<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gegenw<ex>er</ex>tig</expan>
<expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iste</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>es</expan> Wek von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        gnedigisten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem
                            <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. kunig, etlich brief und
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bracht, darinn
                                <expan>und<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ding<ex>en</ex></expan> berürt ist, daz
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der kunig an uns
                            <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan>, dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> zu tun, wan er in in seinr
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<add>zu</add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, den kunig von Engelland, <add>gesant hab;
                            also</add> hat uns <add><expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan></add> diener
                        gebetten umb <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> an ewr
                                <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>. <expan>Bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, daz ir ewch
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iste</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>es</expan> zuvoran von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>r<ex>ömischen</ex></expan>
<expan>k<ex>ünigs</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und auch umb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> befolhen lasset sein und ewr
                                <expan>furdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> tuet. Als etc. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
